    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering with this E46 M3. Powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, this unit features individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Power is channeled through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. This driver-focused example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including VANOS timing adjustment and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry is preserved with refreshed bushings and performance-valved dampers, ensuring the communicative steering and lateral stability the M-chassis is known for. A mechanically robust icon for the serious driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
