      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a driver seeking a blend of performance and reliability. The exterior finish remains vibrant and deep, showing only the minor, superficial road-wear one would expect from a car that has been driven with care. All body panels are straight, and the trim remains crisp. Inside, the cabin is a clean, smoke-free environment where the premium materials have aged gracefully; the seating remains supportive, and every electronic feature\u2014from the climate control to the infotainment system\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the car has been maintained with an open checkbook. It starts promptly, idles smoothly, and delivers power consistently across the rev range. Recent service records are available, confirming that the fluids, filters, and brakes are all in top shape. With a set of high-quality tires showing significant tread, this car is ready for immediate long-distance travel or daily commuting without the need for additional investment.",
      "price": 34500.0,
